<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It seems Zend_Filter doesn't allow (white)spaces in a string. This is rather annoying when you're performing database queries where the spaces are removed from the string and then put into the database.</p>

<p>Is there a way around this, like adding an option to the filter? If not, please allow (white)spaces to the Alnum and Alpha filtering in Zend_Filter.</p>

    </div>
